trans-unit.source: The StripLinesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects, and is implemented as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> class.
trans-unit.target: De klasse StripLinesCollection vertegenwoordigt een verzameling <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>objecten, en wordt ge√Ømplementeerd als de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A>eigenschap van de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects can be appended, inserted or removed from the collection at both design time and run time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>objecten worden toegevoegd, ingevoegd of verwijderd uit de verzameling op zowel ontwerpen en uitvoering.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>

trans-unit.source: **Note** Strip lines can be displayed once or repeatedly for a set interval.
